title: A Clockwork Ley-Line: The Borderline of Dusk
description: Leap into the world of magic, sorcery and the unknown in Unison Shift's A Clockwork Ley-Line: The Borderline of Dusk.This is a Japanese modern fantasy adventure game/visual novel.Featuring gorgeous artwork and great voice acting, the story unravels as you join the journey into the world of Ley-Line.Koga Michiru is a newly enrolled first-year student at a academy with a notably large clock tower located deep in the mountains.
